{"tid":1305435,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法律上 畀人打你係可以「推開」攻擊者 係一個合理解釋","createTime":"2019-07-11T00:34:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T02:01:22.000Z","uid":13663,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"03e0c0d5baeeff66c77f97895369fbc1ce2b9b9d","tid":1305435,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:34:01.000Z","msg":"記住你唔係同佢打交 你純粹推開佢<br />\n不過幾大力就唔知啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多人仲可以用101拘捕令<br />\n<br />\n刑事訴訟程序條例第221章101條 101A條（作出逮捕時武力的使用等）<br />\n-(1) 任何人於防止罪案時或於進行或協助合法逮捕罪犯或疑犯或非法地不在羈留中的人時，可使用就當時環境而言屬於合理的武力。-(2) 普通法中關於何時為第（1）款所述任何目的而使用武力，即因該目的而屬正當地使用武力的規定，由第（1）款予以取代。<br />\n<br />\n-有關拘捕令俗稱101拘捕令，罪行屬嚴重罪行如行劫、傷人、非禮或强姦。"},{"pid":"3975a147ef31fe93af1557af74f21ed26e279e97","tid":1305435,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:35:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c4d57d646d90549fd3b19cc98aeaaed90783059","tid":1305435,"uid":25831,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:35:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"907f55612565d59d9faf216e3313ea26560be53e","tid":1305435,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:36:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bbe70d1dbc09076cfd6edff98dc8ed1ec53f2746","tid":1305435,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:39:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20070602/7167525\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20070602%2F7167525&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJnV%2BAd7ywbQ%2FyO%2FBW%2BNKOVGM%3D&h=13aa9e6e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20070602%2F7167525&h=93efafc8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20070602/7167525</a